Definition: a surgical instrument consisting of wire hoop that can be drawn tight around the base of polyps or small tumors to sever them
Example: used especially in body cavities
Synonyms: surgical_instrument, a, surgical, instrument, consisting, of, wire, hoop, that, can, be, drawn, tight, around, the, base, polyps, or, small, tumors, to, sever, them, used, especially, in, body, cavities
Category: noun.artifact
